PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1784371686
OL,3,CTwo jailed after hacking of Transport
OL,4,Cfor London systems cost #29m in losses
OL,6,FTwo "talented" hackers have been
OL,7,Fjailed after forcing Transport for
OL,8,FLondon to "pull the plug" on their own
OL,9,Fsystems and costing the organisation
OL,10,F#29 million in losses.
OL,12,FThalha Jubair, 20, and Owen Flowers,
OL,13,F18, conducted an "extremely serious
OL,14,Fhack" on TfL's online network which
OL,15,Fcould have caused "catastrophic
OL,16,Fdamage" to their systems between
OL,17,FAugust 31 and September 3 2024.
OL,26,@nD@EOUnD@NO]pD@KOUpD@YO]uD@ROUvD@EO]wD@
OL,26,ASOUxD@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
