OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1784371686
OL,3,CTwo jailed after hacking of Transport
OL,4,Cfor London systems cost #29m in losses
OL,6,FThe "multi-day intrusion" meant all of
OL,7,FTfL's more than 27,000 employees were
OL,8,Fforced to attend an office in person
OL,9,Fto reset their passwords.
OL,11,FIn a sentencing hearing on Wednesday,
OL,12,Fthe prosecution said the hackers
OL,13,F"could have shut out and shut down TfL
OL,14,Fcompletely" as they eventually had the
OL,15,F"highest privileged access" in the
OL,16,Fsystem, known as "the keys to the
OL,17,Fkingdom".
OL,26,@nD@EOUnD@YO]uD@AOUvD@KO]wD@AOUwD@[O]xD@
OL,26,AROUyD@HO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1784371686
OL,3,CTwo jailed after hacking of Transport
OL,4,Cfor London systems cost #29m in losses
OL,6,FMark Fenhalls KC, prosecuting, said:
OL,7,F"These two young men are highly
OL,8,Fskilled with computers and capable of
OL,9,Fwreaking havoc and you may think
OL,10,Fwholly indifferent to the consequences
OL,11,Ffor the public and the potential
OL,12,Fsuffering and costs to others."
OL,14,FData from the Oyster refund system was
OL,15,Faccessed, contactless systems were
OL,16,Fdelayed and applications for Oyster
OL,17,Fphotocards for children and young
OL,18,Fpeople were closed down.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@_O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1784371686
OL,3,CTwo jailed after hacking of Transport
OL,4,Cfor London systems cost #29m in losses
OL,6,FAt Woolwich Crown Court on Thursday,
OL,7,FJubair and Flowers were each jailed
OL,8,Ffor five years and six months.
OL,10,FIn a televised sentencing, Mr Justice
OL,11,FTurner addressed the defendants and
OL,12,Fsaid: "I'm satisfied that your actions
OL,13,Fwere primarily motivated by selfish
OL,14,Fbravado heedless of the consequences
OL,15,Fon others."
OL,17,FThe defendants have been linked to the
OL,18,FScattered Spider, and used that name
OL,19,Fin communication with each other
OL,20,Fduring the attack, the court heard.
OL,26,@tD@GOUwD@KO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1784371686
OL,3,CTwo jailed after hacking of Transport
OL,4,Cfor London systems cost #29m in losses
OL,6,FAlong with the #29 million in damages
OL,7,Ffrom disruption to services and
OL,8,Foperational work, TfL claims the
OL,9,Fincident cost #10 million in lost
OL,10,Fincome.
OL,12,FThe hackers worked through the night
OL,13,Ffor 16 hours to access the TfL systems
OL,14,Fafter tricking the helpdesk into
OL,15,Fresetting a password for them, the
OL,16,Fcourt heard.
OL,18,FThey then logged on to Microsoft Azure
OL,19,Fand began "using TfL's own systems to
OL,20,Fhack itself" as they moved up through
OL,21,Fthe system.
OL,26,@{D@KOU|D@LO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1784371686
OL,3,CTwo jailed after hacking of Transport
OL,4,Cfor London systems cost #29m in losses
OL,6,F"They are both experienced and
OL,7,Ftalented hackers who were together in
OL,8,Fconcert with others to attack TfL,"
OL,9,Fsaid Mr Fenhalls.
OL,11,FFlowers livestreamed Jubair as he
OL,12,Fconducted the hack and some of the
OL,13,Fvideos were recovered when he was
OL,14,Farrested three days later on September
OL,15,F6.
OL,17,FThe pair were in constant contact
OL,18,Fduring the attack and spoke about
OL,19,F"nuking access" to the servers on
OL,20,Ftheir way out.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@cO]{D@AOU{D@OO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1784371686
OL,3,CTwo jailed after hacking of Transport
OL,4,Cfor London systems cost #29m in losses
OL,6,FThe prosecution said the pair were
OL,7,F"utterly reckless about the
OL,8,Fconsequences" and underlined a
OL,9,Fpotential loss of billions to the UK
OL,10,Fif the hackers had locked or destroyed
OL,11,Fthe central TfL system.
OL,13,FIn a victim impact statement read out
OL,14,Fin court on Wednesday, TfL said they
OL,15,Fbelieved the hackers had "sufficient
OL,16,Faccess" during the attack "to cause
OL,17,Fcatastrophic damage to many technology
OL,18,Fsystems, which would have led to
OL,19,Fsignificant and extended transport
OL,20,Fservice degradation and disruption".
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@MO]wD@ZOUxD@GO]xD@[OU|D@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1784371686
OL,3,CTwo jailed after hacking of Transport
OL,4,Cfor London systems cost #29m in losses
OL,6,FMr Fenhalls said: "TfL effectively
OL,7,Fpulled the plug on their own systems,
OL,8,Fthey disconnected all computer
OL,9,Fconnectivity to the internet.
OL,11,F"It was the only thing at that point
OL,12,Fthat they could have done to remove
OL,13,Fthe threat from the system and prevent
OL,14,Fa catastrophe."
OL,16,FDefending Jubair, Paul Keleher KC
OL,17,Fcompared his client to a "modern-day
OL,18,FOliver Twist" who had been groomed
OL,19,Ffrom a young age to use his skills for
OL,20,Fhacking.
OL,26,@nD@SOUsD@AOUvD@OO]yD@ZOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1784371686
OL,3,CTwo jailed after hacking of Transport
OL,4,Cfor London systems cost #29m in losses
OL,6,FJubair was sentenced last year for 22
OL,7,Foffences including hacks on
OL,8,Findividuals, telecoms businesses and
OL,9,Fthe City of London Police system, the
OL,10,Fcourt heard.
OL,12,FOn behalf of Flowers, who was 17 when
OL,13,Fhe conducted the hack, Adam Davis KC
OL,14,Fdescribed his client as an "immature
OL,15,Fchild trying to show off online".
OL,17,FWhen Flowers was arrested in September
OL,18,F2024, his laptop was found in the
OL,19,Fprocess of hacking two US healthcare
OL,20,Fsystems.
OL,26,@vD@\OUwD@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1784371686
OL,3,CTwo jailed after hacking of Transport
OL,4,Cfor London systems cost #29m in losses
OL,6,FThose hacks were only stopped because
OL,7,Fof the "fortuitous timing" of his
OL,8,Farrest, the court heard.
OL,10,FBoth young men admitted conspiracy to
OL,11,Fcommit unauthorised acts in relation
OL,12,Fto a computer causing or creating risk
OL,13,Fof serious damage.
OL,15,FFlowers also admitted two counts of
OL,16,Fconspiracy to commit unauthorised acts
OL,17,Fin relation to a computer with intent
OL,18,Fto impair, in relation to the
OL,19,Fhealthcare systems.
OL,26,@oD@HOUoD@ZO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/10
